This paper is about the architecture and implementation of a digital library platform, which falls under the category of digital libraries (cs.DL). The paper also discusses the data model and API used in the platform, which relates to information retrieval (cs.IR). Additionally, the paper mentions backend services and frontend tools, which could be categorized under cyberinfrastructure (cs.CY) and computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the paper discusses the use of a digital repository, which is related to database systems (cs.DB).
